Negevs
{Data.map((item) => (
{item.name}
Amount: {item.amount}
Bought for: {item.bought_for}$
Overall benefit: {item.benefit}$ Current price: {item.current_price}$ Percent benefit: +{item.percent_benefit}%

) } export default Bag;
